column5: Nice bro, keep driving safe. Btw i jealous with your country, i'm sure your country has much good drivers on the road, in my country you can have the driver license with just add your data and "pay" them, and then u got the license. That's why in my country road has much drivers who has bad attitude.

Hi mike, thanks for sharing your story to us. This post makes me want to do more in my life even no one supports me, i want to keep struggling through my hard times. Now i realize there is people who have much problem than me, but keep struggling for their happiness, like you.
I hope you happy until the end of time, thank you
